subtasks.subtask:
Define step structure (model, input, output, error handling) với example:
            {
              "steps": [
                {
                  "id": "step_1",
                  "model": "openai-compatible/gpt-4o-mini",
                  "input": "user_query",
                  "prompt_template": "Analyze: {input}",
                  "output_key": "analysis_result",
                  "error_handling": {"retry": 2, "fallback_model": "openai-compatible/qwen3-30b"}
                },
                {
                  "id": "step_2",
                  "model": "openai-compatible/gpt-4o",
                  "input": "{step_1.output_key}",
                  "prompt_template": "Create plan based on: {input}",
                  "output_key": "plan_result"
                }
              ]
            }

interface.signature:
{
        "steps": [
          {
            "id": str,
            "model": str,
            "input": str,
            "prompt_template": str,
            "output_key": str,
            "error_handling": Optional[Dict[str, Any]]
          }
        ]
      }
